name: Rachnera Arachnera(MonsterMusume)
description:
Edit: Let's call this an Rachnera Cospaly. Not sure if I can figure out how to properly do the spider bits....
I realized that no one had done this yet and I someone who owns a Rachnee mousepad, it bothered me. I left her hair color, eye color, and extra eyes be baked in because it felt right. What is a spider waifu without 6 red eyes to watch you? The classic outfit will need some additional work but it sometimes works.

Notes:

  • Strength of 1.0 seems perfectly fine

  • Number of extra eyes tends towards 4 but can be more

  • The LoRA can omit her spider body but is weighted towards it because, like of course.

  • Some this parts of the image look kinda oil paintingy. No idea why

Trigger word: rachnera_arachnera

Helpful words: large_breasts, multiple_legs, claws, taur
